    <body>Converts the cursor to Cursor mode, which lets you add a cursor bitmap to the frame by clicking in the frame and dragging in any direction. When you release the mouse button, a cursor bitmap is added within a shaded oval shape. You can change the cursor type and adjust the color and transparency of the oval background from the Cursor section in the Object Properties window pane. See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Objects/Cursors/Adding_Cursors.htm">Adding Cursors</MadCap:xref>.</body>
